Invocation Name: presidential alert
des: This app is a parody to the 1st Test Presidential Alert that went out to all US citizens on October 3rd, 2018. This app is intended to be for fun, and is not affiliated with the US Government in any way. This is also not a real emergency alert system. This is just for fun. Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
